{"tid":2505114,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【ViuTV一哥】強尼棄當工程師賣樓入行追夢　感激太太零怨言當最大後盾","createTime":"2021-04-26T10:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T11:14:05.000Z","uid":350584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f711b89d22ae13c01b48fa4f3b1ce44e67621c36","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:56:19.000Z","msg":"ViuTV選秀節目《全民造星III》大受歡迎，除令眾參賽者人氣急升外，《全民造星III》主持強尼亦人氣高企，再加當時有劇集《暖男爸爸》的播出，一眾網民更封強尼做ViuTV一哥。<br />\n<br />\n強尼接受商台《1圈圈星光背後》訪問，表示主持《全民造星》節目系列確實令他的事業及收入增加。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oU7himF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoU7himF.jpg&h=7ed821b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dbb53f90032b3a8863c13c36c75a7d8d2d87c35","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:56:38.000Z","msg":"建築師轉行做主持<br />\n<br />\n強尼（許博文）早於2004年已入行，初期有線電視娛樂台擔任《夢幻建築社》及《空間大改造》系列節目主持，並曾演出《我要結婚》、《呢份咩野工》。<br />\n<br />\n2016年，他加入FOX體育台擔任足球評述員，並於ViuTV出任藝員及節目主持，至2020年起參與劇集及音樂節目演出，人氣急升。他稱：「這半年收入是多了，的確是因為觀眾留意《全民造星》的年青人間接留意到我，讓客知道有選擇。」"},{"pid":"305bb1bb3245fe4109f816e8bed12bded9332765","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:56:52.000Z","msg":"入行前，強尼畢業於城市大學工程系，是有樓有老婆的建築工程師。不過，自小熱愛足球與音樂的他不甘一輩子做工程師，決定放棄安穩工作入行追夢：「我不像身邊同學們般醉心研究起樓，他們很有熱誠，我預計自己在這行的發展唔叻，只是單純想嘗試其他發展。」"},{"pid":"0a31deec013e9ce4a6111c989c02f97a4f75c4ad","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"太太家人支持賣樓追夢<br />\n<br />\n當時，他碰巧遇上有線請講波，更無需經驗，於是寫信應徵。他指當時太太的反應從未有質疑，更輕鬆幫我寄信指：「你真的嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n後來，在不少親慼聚會中，太太及父母也常被問及：「他為何有工程師唔做去講波？」，但三人都一致支持強尼繼續追夢：「好吖！試吓吖！」"},{"pid":"b010739b0b2068ff72027d15bc66df8fa1a61d27","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d3GaDm6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd3GaDm6.jpg&h=d602b95f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強尼育有一子。"},{"pid":"0c02e17c947865cd455747a0eca5aff73f0801d5","tid":2505114,"uid":36049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:57:52.000Z","msg":"全能到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad65cd08bc4dda86ad0ba14416f091fb52c86895","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:57:52.000Z","msg":"強尼由兼職變全職，更賣樓全身投入娛圈做主持，他直言當時年青甚麼都夠膽嘗試外，也要感謝太太及父母一直支持做他的後盾：「我27歲結婚，太太本身是秘書，是於我第一間任職建築公司認識。她從來無埋怨，也從沒著眼於金錢跟物質生活上。」<br />\n<br />\n他續指：「當然十幾年來，我們會不斷檢視，我也有不順利高低起跌有情緒的時刻，她只會說：『放心呀！要是再不順利，大不了可出返來做建築由低做起？』」"},{"pid":"d83a324fd003f4783ce7ea0198099df6d0152854","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:58:10.000Z","msg":"憑《造星》人氣急升<br />\n<br />\n而且強尼一直堅持做這一行全因這份工是他的最愛：「我真的鍾意做，亦覺得自己有能力去做，我認為自己做主持叻過起樓，運用我的擅長做可以做的工作是首選，次選才是建築。」 <br />\n<br />\n轉行入行17年，強尼由2016年起轉投ViuTV，曾視為演藝工作最後機會的他，終憑主持《全民造星》彈起，嘗試劇集及音樂發展，贏得觀眾認同。"},{"pid":"6852736a587c14e0bf508d8a13855abbe4a13803","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"強尼幾近與MIRROR一同彈出，看著姜濤Mirror等揚威《叱咤》，他指感覺奇妙：「最初第一輯《造星》，我相信觀眾會想笑這班年青人，而當中有些的確是很好笑。到三、四年後，看著他們會變成頒獎禮一股新力量，是很神奇！」<br />\n<br />\n他又分析姜濤或Mirror的成功，在於新一代觀眾接受有瑕疵的偶像，再願意陪伴他們成長，更懂接納，故才累積到一班不會走的忠心粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z0LyA9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ0LyA9c.jpg&h=ba7363b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"202fb53951d6ab1d79cf7208dcec65a77e5c9931","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:00:07.000Z","msg":"他又分析姜濤或Mirror的成功，在於新一代觀眾接受有瑕疵的偶像，再願意陪伴他們成長，更懂接納，故才累積到一班不會走的忠心粉絲。<br />\n<br />\n講得好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b24764580dcde1ecc5e95ecf1206d64f941674","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3CjodXB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3CjodXB.jpg&h=f9394cb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強尼和Ali曾為有線節目《空間大改造》主持。（《空間大改造》截圖）"},{"pid":"bd07adef889e0271113b98c82c8e4945665a3831","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iSMRnQ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiSMRnQ8.jpg&h=b14464cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強尼身兼足球評述員。"},{"pid":"6d3989c809752e487ab6f9a095d46e98ea15e980","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i1MYNh0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi1MYNh0.jpg&h=e2e0e276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強尼入行後曾回到建築行業一年半。"},{"pid":"b4ce9e5606155e924a62036862af3588b8a89a3f","tid":2505114,"uid":292497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"全尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢做主持真係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca329bd0b47212441382f3ed2a4cc2146077f016","tid":2505114,"uid":350584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4ce9e5606155e924a62036862af3588b8a89a3f","tid":2505114,"uid":292497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"全尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢做主持真係幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"全能的強尼"}]}